dfischer.utils

Class InnerLoopContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • dfischer.utils.InnerLoopContext

  • public class InnerLoopContext
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class used to support "continue" and "break" of inner loops. This class is only used when the load test program is generated by using the "large code model".

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      InnerLoopContext()
      Create a new instance an initialize the "continue loop flag" and "break loop flag" with a value of false.
